  npcPotrait: {fileID: -8406110673211288041, guid: 8ad9f71c0e215ab4a98a7a2e0e6624a1, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Are you looking for someone?
  - "\u201CBhishi.\u201D "
  - "There are 12 of us. Each month, \u20B93,000."
  - "Total \u20B936,000.Every month, one person takes the full amount"
  - Sometimes we draw lots.Sometimes we bid.
  - Sometimes urgency decides.
  - "That\u2019s why this exists."
  - "If your turn comes early\u2026"
  - You get access before saving the full amount yourself.
  - That is risk.We choose members carefully.
  - We choose members carefully.Trust matters.
  - "Before banks gave loans\u2026"
  - "Before apps\u2026We relied on each other."
  - "Both.\u201D \u201CIf your turn is last\u2026\u201D  \u201CYou saved slowly.\u201D"
  - "If your turn is first\u2026\u201D  \u201CYou borrowed from the group.\u201D "
  - "Safer than borrowing from strangers.\u201D  \u201CLess safe than a bank"
  - "Banks run on contracts.\u201D  \u201CWe run on reputation.\u201D"
